Class ArrayList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • collections.ArrayList<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of ArrayList
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    List<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class ArrayList<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements List<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>
    Resizable-array implementation of the List interface. Where user can add, remove element, get and set element in diffrent positions.
    Author:
    Sebastian Börebäck
